Xtreme Couture Presents...MASTERS OF MMA - Randy Couture's: Wrestling For Fighting.  MMA legend and UFC Hall of Famer, Randy "The Natural" Couture takes you through the sport of MMA with his latest project "Wrestling For Fighting."  Training techniques, wrestling stories, strategies, attitude all covered by the master himself.  

Check out the trailer!  

"Pain is temporary...Pride is forever" ~Randy "The Natural" Couture
